          <ul class=\"pickup-nav-c\">\r\n              <li><a href=\"https://www.pref.aichi.jp/soshiki/jinji-syokuin/nittei-zyukennannai.html\"><span>日程・受験案内</span></a></li>\r\n              <li><a href=\"https://www.pref.aichi.jp/soshiki/jinji-syokuin/sikenkekka.html\"><span>試験結果</span></a></li>\r\n              <li><a href=\"https://www.pref.aichi.jp/soshiki/kenminseikatsu/0000017554.html\"><span>試験結果の閲覧方法</span></a></li>\r\n              <li><a href=\"https://www.pref.aichi.jp/soshiki/jinji-syokuin/sikenmondai-reidai.html\"><span>試験問題の例題</span></a></li>\r\n            </ul>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </li>\r\n        <li class=\"pickup-list-item\">\r\n          <figure><img src=\"assets/img/home/pickup_p06.jpg\" alt=\"説明会情報の画像\" class=\"w100\"></figure>\r\n          <div class=\"pickup-nav\">\r\n            <p class=\"pickup-nav-p\">説明会情報</p>\r\n            <ul class=\"pickup-nav-c\">\r\n              <li><a href=\"https://www.pref.aichi.jp/soshiki/jinji-syokuin/guidance-entry.html\"><span>職員ガイダンス</span></a></li>\r\n              <li><a href=\"https://www.pref.aichi.jp/soshiki/jinji-syokuin/toukai-hokuriku-seminar.html\"><span>東海・北陸６県庁 公務研究セミナー</span></a></li>\r\n              <li><a href=\"https://www.pref.aichi.jp/soshiki/jinji-syokuin/saiyo-setsumei.html\"><span>採用試験説明会</span></a></li>\r\n              <li><a href=\"https://www.pref.aichi.jp/soshiki/jinji-syokuin/setumeikai.html\"><span>大学・民間企業等主催説明会</span></a></li>\r\n            </ul>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </li>\r\n      </ul>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section class=\"sns-sec js-anime js-anime-fadein\">\r\n  <div class=\"inner\">\r\n    <h2 class=\"mainttl-txt\"><span>愛知県人事委員会ＳＮＳ</span></h2>\r\n    <div class=\"sns-con\">\r\n      <div class=\"sns-box _l\">\r\n        <p class=\"sns-ttl\"><i class=\"ico ico-facebook\"></i><span>Facebook</span></p>\r\n        <div class=\"fb-page\" data-href=\"https://www.facebook.com/aichikenjinjiiinkai\" data-tabs=\"timeline\" data-width=\